{"tid":863268,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)不死J神系列","createTime":"2018-10-15T12:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T19:55:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf16dd4cdb840d8e27a6413d382247f2df6e5b8","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=b371c228\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=254e8fb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=4875942c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/eb/The_Transporter_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Feb%2FThe_Transporter_2_poster.jpg&h=67aec41c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Death_race_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fd2%2FDeath_race_poster.jpg&h=45024480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/93/Crank_two_ver2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F9%2F93%2FCrank_two_ver2.jpg&h=7fa00999&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/47/Parker_2013_Movie_Poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F4%2F47%2FParker_2013_Movie_Poster.png&h=099e190a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.法蘭克&middot;馬丁（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）從法國南部搬遷至美國佛羅里達州邁阿密。出於人情，他暫時擔任有錢人家比令家族的司機。而由於傑佛遜（馬修&middot;摩丁飾）高姿態的政府工作需求，使得他與奧黛麗&middot;比令（琥珀&middot;瓦萊塔飾）的婚姻關係處於高度緊張狀態。法蘭克與比令夫妻就讀小學的兒子傑克（亨特&middot;克拉里飾）相處融洽，並每日駕駛著奧迪A8 W12載他上下學。[2]隨後，稍顯醉意的奧黛麗出現在法蘭克的家中，並且試圖勾引他，但法蘭克機靈地將她送回家<br />\n<br />\n2.2012年，美國經濟全面崩盤，導致失業率乃至犯罪率逐漸失控的情況下，一些富有權貴成立私人監獄來賺錢。其中一處則是「終結島」（Terminal Island）：一座距離內陸長達兩英里的海島監獄，不少死刑犯和終身監禁犯都被拘禁於此。典獄長克萊爾&middot;韓娜席通過網絡直播囚犯角鬥形式的生死決鬥來獲得更多利益，但因觀眾容易失去興趣，於是創立出囚犯互相靠賽車形式競爭的「亡命賽車」（Death Race）<br />\n<br />\n3.職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）為了心愛的未婚妻伊娃（艾咪&middot;史瑪特飾）打算金盆洗手，但是人在江湖飄，哪有不挨刀，就在他想退出江湖時，仇家上門報復，而且是非常特異的手法：在他睡夢中注射一種毒藥，要讓他心臟麻痺而死。契夫在痛苦中求救，終於發現了暫保活命的方法，作極其激烈的運動，讓心臟猛跳，只要心跳一減緩，他就會死。他要如何保住小命，救出被擄走的愛人呢？<br />\n<br />\n4.上一次大難不死的職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）又遇到艱辛萬倍的挑戰，有人將他的心臟奪走，改以一個人工幫浦取代，甚至還有一個不知名的華人黑道組織要取他器官，而這次契夫要一直為自己的幫浦心臟充電，否則就會一命不保，所以他竭盡腦汁，用了變電箱、汽車電池、電擊棒，甚至是靜電來維繫生命，究竟他要如何保住性命，追回自己的心臟呢？<br />\n<br />\n5.派克（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）是一名「盜亦有道」的搶匪，他只搶富人，而且作案絕不傷害善良百姓。一次參加了一個犯罪集團，他打算收手，結束綠林人生，卻慘遭黑喫黑，差點淪為波臣。身負重傷的派克打算報仇，也希望獲得鉅款，金盆洗手，派克四處尋找仇家，希望能拿回他應得的鈔票，卻在因緣際會下，遇上了一位美豔的失婚女房仲經理人萊絲麗（珍妮佛&middot;洛佩茲飾），在若有似無的情愫中，兩人開展合作。派克的計畫是：以其人之道，還治其人之身.... <br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=56a08f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2BleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e099f599\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2179485a5cbf24febfb6b204d1a1032dcc5ec44b","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b560f792b97e03ca8ae4e7b0a94c85b5d426abcd","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330171d4ef4388a0aaed78349077d86df8331f04","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4424ded539e3bda225230a3824a2ea86ccdb79b","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0210c2b51c909bf379f4690cc2df0642b4263c4","tid":863268,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"